============================================================
PROJECT REPORT SUMMARY: EMPLOYEE ATTRITION AI PORTAL
============================================================

1. PROJECT TITLE:
   AI-Driven HR ERP Platform for Attrition Prediction and Loss-Control Management.

2. OBJECTIVE:
   To build an interactive HR system that predicts employee attrition risk using Machine Learning (Random Forest) and automatically calculates cost-effective retention strategies based on employee merits (Attendance, Skills, Knowledge) to prevent company loss.

3. TECH STACK:
   - Language: Python
   - Frontend/UI: Streamlit Framework
   - Machine Learning: Scikit-Learn (Random Forest Classifier)
   - Data Handling: Pandas, NumPy

4. KEY LOGIC INCLUDED:
   - Dynamic Salary Bracket up to $500,000.
   - IT Department & custom tech job roles integration.
   - Company Safeguard: Smart retention offers (Salary Hike, Low Working Hours, Accommodation) are ONLY provided if the employee maintains 90%+ Attendance and Active Skills.